 image input in Telegram/Discord gateway.\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:4:  \"branchName\": \"ralph/vision-support\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:8:      \"title\": \"Config schema — image / vision / context_window 欄位\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:9:      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want to declare image processing strategy and provider vision capability in config so that the pipeline knows how to process images and which providers support them.\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:14:        \"五個 provider config（OpenRouterConfig / AnthropicConfig / OpenAiConfig / ZhipuConfig / LlamaCppConfig）各新增 vision: Option<bool> 和 context_window: Option<usize>\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:15:        \"config.example.toml 補上 [image] section 與各 provider 的 vision / context_window 欄位及中文註解\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:49:      \"title\": \"Domain — Message attachments（session 持久化）\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:50:      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want session messages to carry optional image attachments so that conversation history with images can be persisted and resumed.\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:52:        \"crates/domain/src/message.rs 的 Message struct 新增 attachments: Option<Vec<Attachment>>\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:53:        \"Attachment struct 定義 media_type: String 與 data: AttachmentData\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:54:        \"AttachmentData enum 定義 Base64(String) / Url(String)\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:55:        \"attachments 欄位標注 #[serde(skip_serializing_if = \\\"Option::is_none\\\")]\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:56:        \"舊 session JSON（無 attachments 欄位）仍可正常 deserialize，不 panic\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:69:      \"title\": \"crates/image-process — 新 workspace crate\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:70:      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want a dedicated image-process crate so that image decoding, resizing, and quantization logic is isolated and reusable by both CLI and gateway.\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:72:        \"crates/image-process/ 目錄建立，Cargo.toml 加入 workspace members，依賴：imagequant = \\\"4\\\", png = \\\"0.17\\\", image = { version = \\\"*\\\", features = [\\\"png\\\", \\\"jpeg\\\", \\\"webp\\\", \\\"gif\\\"] }\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:113:        \"crates/ports/src/provider.rs 新增 ProviderCapabilities { vision: bool, context_window: Option<usize> }\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:115:        \"ProviderRouter（crates/provider/src/router.rs）實作 capabilities()，採 conservative merge：任一 provider vision = false 則整體回傳 false\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:116:        \"所有現有 adapter（openrouter / anthropic / openai / zhipu / llamacpp）先實作此方法回傳 vision: false, context_window: None（後續 US-006~010 覆寫）\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:132:      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want the OpenRouter adapter to support vision so that images can be sent to OpenRouter vision-capable models.\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:134:        \"OpenRouterAdapter 建構時從 OpenRouterConfig.vision 讀值並存起來\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:135:        \"capabilities() 正確回傳 config 宣告的 vision 與 context_window\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:138:        \"vision = false 時 adapter 行為與現在完全相同\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:155:      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want the Anthropic adapter to support vision using Anthropic's native image format.\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:157:        \"AnthropicAdapter 建構時從 AnthropicConfig.vision 讀值並存起來\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:158:        \"capabilities() 正確回傳 config 宣告的 vision 與 context_window\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:161:        \"vision = false 時 adapter 行為與現在完全相同\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:178:      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want the OpenAI adapter to support vision.\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:180:        \"OpenAiAdapter 建構時從 OpenAiConfig.vision 讀值並存起來\",\ntasks/prd-vision-support.json:181:        \"capabilities() 正確回傳 config 宣告的 vision 與 context_window\",