ct.\ncrates/application/src/kairos_acceptance_tests.rs:603:                trigger: ModeSwitchTrigger::SlashCommand,\ncrates/application/src/kairos_acceptance_tests.rs:607:        \"switch event with SlashCommand trigger expected\"\nCargo.toml:18:    \"crates/image-process\",\nCargo.toml:46:reqwest            = { version = \"0.12\", features = [\"json\", \"stream\"] }\ndocs/acceptance-spec.md:120:3. Memory footprint under sustained interaction.\ncrates/application/src/error.rs:11:    #[error(\"vision is not supported by provider: {0}\")]\ncrates/application/src/error.rs:12:    VisionNotSupported(String),\ncrates/application/src/ultraplan_acceptance_tests.rs:316:    let slash_result = service\ncrates/application/src/ultraplan_acceptance_tests.rs:320:        matches!(slash_result, Err(UltraplanError::AlreadyActive)),\ncrates/application/src/ultraplan_acceptance_tests.rs:321:        \"slash-keyword launch while active returns AlreadyActive\"\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:1:# Gateway Webhook Daemon — Telegram & Discord\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:5:**Goal:** 新增 `crates/gateway/` binary crate，作為 long-running HTTP daemon，接收來自 Telegram 和 Discord 的 webhook/interaction 訊息，驅動 `AgentRunCommand` 執行並回覆。\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:7:**Architecture:** `gateway` 與 `cli` 並列，同樣依賴 `ccode-bootstrap`。Axum 作為 HTTP server（已是 workspace 依賴）。設定透過 `~/.ccode/config.toml` 的 `[gateway]` section 管理，CLI flag 可覆蓋 port 和 workdir。Discord 需要 Ed25519 簽名驗證（新增 `ed25519-dalek` 依賴）。\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:19:[gateway.discord]\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:20:application_public_key = \"abcdef...\"  # Discord Developer Portal 的 Ed25519 公鑰\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:24:**Tech Stack:** Rust (`axum 0.7`, `tokio`, `ed25519-dalek 2`, `reqwest`)，現有 `AgentRunCommand`，現有 `wire_from_config_with_cwd`。\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:34:2. 新增 `GatewayConfig` struct（`port: Option<u16>`, `workdir: Option<String>`, `telegram: Option<TelegramConfig>`, `discord: Option<DiscordConfig>`）。\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:36:4. 新增 `DiscordConfig` struct（`application_public_key: String`, `bot_token: Option<String>`）。\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:46:1. `Cargo.toml` 依賴：`ccode-bootstrap`, `ccode-config`, `axum`, `tokio`（`rt-multi-thread`+`macros`+`signal`）, `serde`, `serde_json`, `tracing`, `tracing-subscriber`, `thiserror`, `anyhow`, `reqwest`, `clap`, `ed25519-dalek = \"2\"`, `hex = \"0.4\"`。\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:76:6. 用 `reqwest` 呼叫 `https://api.telegram.org/bot{token}/sendMessage`，payload：`{\"chat_id\": ..., \"text\": ...}`。\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:79:### Task 5: 實作 adapters/discord — Interactions handler\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:82:- Create: `crates/gateway/src/adapters/discord.rs`\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:84:1. 定義必要型別：`DiscordInteraction`（`type: u8`, `data: Option<DiscordInteractionData>`, `token: String`, `channel_id: Option<String>`）。\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:85:2. **Ed25519 簽名驗證**（Discord 強制要求）：\ndocs/plans/2026-04-06-gateway-webhook-daemon.md:105:   - `POST /webhook/discord`  → `adapters::discord::handle`（條件：`gateway_cfg.discord.is_some()`，否則回 `404`）\ndocs/integration-contracts.md:41:3. Sync retries and watcher behavior must not block user interaction loops.\nREADME.zh.md:55:`ccode-gateway` 是一個長時間運行的 HTTP daemon，接收來自通訊平台（Telegram、Discord）的訊息並驅動 agent 執行。\nREADME.zh.md:78:| POST   | `/webhook/discord`    | Discord interactions 端點                   |\nREADME.zh.md:108:### Discord 設定步驟\nREADME.zh.md:110:1. 前往 [Discord Developer Portal](https://discord.com/developers/applications)，建立一個 Application。\nREADME.zh.md:112:3. 在 **Interactions Endpoint URL** 填入 `https://your-domain/webhook/discord`，儲存。\nREADME.zh.md:113:   - Discord 會發送 PING（type 1）驗證端點，gateway 自動回應 PONG。\nREADME.zh.md:114:4.